  "description": "The original Minecraft texture feel, with double the resolution and double the fun!",
  "body": "<center>\n\t<img style=\"width: 1142px;\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/wordmarks/outlined/cracked/f32_wordmark.png\">\n\t<h1>The go-to 32x resource pack for Minecraft.</h1>\n\t<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft-bedrock/addons/faithful-32x-bedrock\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img\n\t\t\tstyle=\"width: 1142px;\"\n\t\t\tsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/bedrock_button.png\"\n\t\t\talt=\"Get the Bedrock pack here\"\n\t\t>\n\t</a>\n</center>\n<hr>\n<p>\n    The one and only, Faithful 32x boasts a modern, detailed art style that focuses on reimagining textures instead of simply redrawing them, \n    taking full advantage of the higher resolution. Its notable features include a limited palette and a strive for consistency.\n\t<br><br>\n    The pack has evolved tremendously over the years. Ever since it was originally started by Vattic all the way back in 2010,\n     it has become a cultural icon and has been enjoyed by millions of Minecraft players. Ready to become one of them?\n\n</p>\n<center>\n\t<a href=\"https://discord.gg/sN9YRQbBv7\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img style=\"width: 1142px;\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/discord_button.png\" alt=\"Discord Server\">\n\t</a>\n  <br><br>\n\t<a href=\"https://faithfulpack.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img style=\"width: 1142px;\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/website_button.png\" alt=\"Website\">\n\t</a>\n</center>\n<hr>\n<center><h2>Additional Information:</h2></center>\n<p>\n\tIf you have any feedback, want to report a bug, or generally need help,\n\tjoin our <a href=\"https://discord.gg/sN9YRQbBv7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Discord</a> server above, make a\n\t<a href=\"https://github.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Faithful-32x-Java/issues\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">GitHub issue</a>,\n\tor comment below. For any commercial or distribution-related questions, refer to our\n\t<a href=\"http://faithfulpack.net/license\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">license</a>.\n\t<br><br>\n\tAll textures and add-ons are provided by contributors volunteering in their free time.\n\tAnyone can submit textures through our Discord server linked above, or make an\n\t<a href=\"http://faithfulpack.net/addons\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">add-on</a>\n\tto officially list on our website. Before you begin, make sure to read our\n\t<a href=\"https://docs.faithfulpack.net/pages/textures/f32-texturing-guidelines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">texturing guidelines</a>\n\twhich precisely outline the art style of the pack.\n\t<br><br>\n\tEach pack has listings on our <a href=\"faithfulpack.net\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">website</a>,\n\t<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/faithful_resource_pack/projects\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CurseForge</a>,\n\t<a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/member/faithful_resource_pack/submissions/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Planet Minecraft</a>,\n\tand <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Faithful-Resource-Pack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Modrinth</a>,\n\tand some packs are additionally listed on <a href=\"https://mcpedl.com/user/faithful-resource-pack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MCPEDL</a>\n\tand the <a href=\"https://www.minecraftforum.net/members/Faithful_Resource_Pack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Minecraft Forums</a>.\n\t<strong>Downloads from any other sites are unofficial, unsupported and could be dangerous!</strong>\n\tRemember to stay safe on the internet.\n</p>\n<hr>\n<center><h2>Our Other Projects:</h2></center>\n<div style=\"text-align: center\">\n\t<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/faithful-64x\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img\n\t\t\tstyle=\"width: 1142px;\"\n\t\t\tsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/f64_button.png\"\n\t\t\talt=\"Faithful 64x\"\n\t\t>\n\t</a>\n\t<br><br>\n\t<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/classic-faithful-32x\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img\n\t\t\tstyle=\"width: 1142px;\"\n\t\t\tsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/cf32_button.png\"\n\t\t\talt=\"Classic Faithful 32x\"\n\t\t>\n\t</a>\n\t<br><br>\n\t<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/classic-faithful-32x-jappa\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img\n\t\t\tstyle=\"width: 1142px;\"\n\t\t\tsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/cf32j_button.png\"\n\t\t\talt=\"Classic Faithful 32x Jappa\"\n\t\t>\n\t</a>\n\t<br><br>\n\t<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/classic-faithful-64x\" rel=\"nofollow\">\n\t\t<img\n\t\t\tstyle=\"width: 1142px;\"\n\t\t\tsrc=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Faithful-Resource-Pack/Branding/main/social_media/buttons/cf64j_button.png\"\n\t\t\talt=\"Classic Faithful 64x Jappa\"\n\t\t>\n\t</a>\n</div>",
